# Master-best-files vault

The **Master-best-files** folder is for team-approved material (prompts, templates, snippets, etc.).

- **Do not** create, copy, move, or save files into **Master-best-files** unless the user **explicitly** asked to put something there (e.g. “sync this to the master folder,” “add the approved version to Master-best-files,” “copy into the vault”).
- Drafting, iteration, and experiments stay in **personal or project folders** until a clear promote/sync instruction is given.

If unsure, ask once instead of writing to this folder.
